<li>Gann, Kyle. 2001. "<a href="http://www.newmusicbox.org/article.nmbx?id=1536" class="external text" title="http://www.newmusicbox.org/article.nmbx?id=1536" rel="nofollow">Minimal Music, Maximal Impact: Minimalism's Immediate Legacy: Postminimalism</a>". <i>New Music Box: The Web Magazine from the American Music Center</i> (November 1).</li>
